:FED.1.2 &WEBSYSNAVN.:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
&WEBSYSNAVN. is a payment service subject to the rules
set out in the Danish Payment Service and Electronic Money Act (lov om
betalingstjenester og elektroniske penge).
The Act also applies to payment transactions processed in the
customer's payment accounts in &WEBSYSNAVN.. &WEBSYSNAVN. also allows the
customer to electronically conclude and approve other agreements with
&BANKNAVN. Agreements concluded and approved electronically are not
considered payment services unless so stipulated in the specific agreement.
.sp 3mm
