suffered by the customer, including operating loss, loss of interest, loss
of time, loss of goodwill or for damage to the customer s property,
including loss of data or programs, not even if such damage is due to a
defect in &BANKNAVN. s product. This applies irrespective of whether
&BANKNAVN. has been informed of the risk of such loss, or whether
&BANKNAVN. has acted negligently.
